description:
&lt;p&gt;The trust is looking for a dynamic individual to lead as the matron for the new AAU and 35 bedded medical ward . As part of our expansion the trust has invested in an new Acute Assessment Unit for all patients waiting to be assessed by specialty teams, as well as a 35 bed medical ward for patients within the first 72 hours of their care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a person who will develop the teams to deliver world class care within the two new units. You will be supported by a senior matron and a divisional nurse director. If you think this exciting opportunity is for you, then please apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Kay Gilsenan&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: kay.gilsenan@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
